ledgersmb-1.6 (1.6.6-2~1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Add '05_Makefile.patch' to facilitate running the upstream basic tests
    during a package build.
  * Add 'texlive-latex-recommended' to the Build-Depends in debian/control.
  * Derive the Build-Depends-Indep stanza from the Depends and Recommends in
    the debian/control file.
  * Remove the 'override_dh_auto_test' target from debian/rules to facilitate
    the running of basic upstream tests during a package build.
  * Explicitly add 'libdata-uuid-perl', 'libplack-middleware-reverseproxy-perl',
    and 'libtext-markdown-perl' to the Depends stanza in debian/control.

